c: 48
v: 10
t: "Inene abo benza isifungo sesibophelelo kuwe (Muhammad) bona enyanisweni benza isifungo sesibophelelo kuAllâh. ISandla sika-Allâh siphezu kwezandla zabo. Ke lowo waphula isithembiso sakhe, usaphula ngokuchasene nesiqu sakhe. Lowo uzalisekisa oko athembise ngako kuAllâh, (uAllâh) Uya kumnika umvuzo omkhulu"